abstract: >-
  A single repository integrating 5 independent AI rule systems (coding,
  conversation, novel, interactive-novel, agent-builder) with a shared core
  layer, 13 composable capability packs, and multi-tool sync (Claude Code,
  Gemini, Cursor, GitHub Copilot, Trae). Incorporates research-backed prompt
  engineering and safety guardrails.
